{"tid":995740,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟應該點解讀生命同時間呢樣概念？","createTime":"2019-01-25T16:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T01:44:15.000Z","uid":195396,"like":34,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"11782729d88cebad9b2d35938a89cde0907330e4","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"頭先睇到時事台個post有感<br />\n人生在世幾十年 好彩嘅都係得一百年<br />\n我就成日講 你點生活都好 一日都係廿四個鐘 時間都係咁樣過<br />\n但係時間呢個概念係點得嚟㗎呢<br />\n點解一秒係一秒<br />\n如果太陽/地球 somehow轉慢咗 一秒仲係咪一秒？<br />\n<br />\n再推遠啲<br />\n點解會有人諗到有時間呢樣嘢？<br />\n如果我哋無回憶 無期盼 仲會唔會有時間呢個概念？<br />\n<br />\n拉埋生命嚟講<br />\n我覺得<br />\n回憶同未來嘅嘢都係虛構嘅 只有當下係真<br />\n但係我諗以人腦嘅運算速度無可能捉得住當下呢個點<br />\n咁係咪姐係我哋成個生命都係虛構？<br />\n<br />\n諗到呢度<br />\n就好想知道死後嘅世界又會係點樣<br />\n如果時間呢個概念係又人類提出嚟<br />\n死後係咪suppose唔會有時間呢樣嘢？（當然假設死咗仲有意識）<br />\n<br />\n如果講到1999 或者有咩出錯 有咩on9 講聲sorry 因為我真係純粹無聊先會諗呢啲嘢<br />\n平時都無研究呢方面 無睇書無上堂<br />\n<br />\n希望有人指教吓 交流吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e240602c12e443b5a75982ace57a4280301559","tid":995740,"uid":229977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"08a28de47c0b0fcca9f5872d86345387251bd553","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88e240602c12e443b5a75982ace57a4280301559","tid":995740,"uid":229977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:42:03.000Z","msg":"交流吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3393fb134c17bfc41a3563992e90cbe66052ce61","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"btw 如果有師兄有研究開呢方面可唔可以介紹啲書嚟睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c188d338267b92721a5c56a873b209b7a271513","tid":995740,"uid":89514,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67c8590fd7d79135aac34e196b572f444535cae0","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c188d338267b92721a5c56a873b209b7a271513","tid":995740,"uid":89514,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"此話何解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8253a03fcc3b39fe85276d215e0243d18dd4f6","tid":995740,"uid":232363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"問下哲學老師"},{"pid":"4237a939c3ff8c495cfcaf740d91eac91fe8c620","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e8253a03fcc3b39fe85276d215e0243d18dd4f6","tid":995740,"uid":232363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"問下哲學老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:51:10.000Z","msg":"無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做緊廢青"},{"pid":"23da5557fa306ff5052c7dba6d3003342c1fdbd1","tid":995740,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"我都相信時間只係人發明出黎既概念<br />\n世界本無時間 只有此時此刻 一直運轉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死後既世界更多關於信仰既問題？"},{"pid":"6468da49f111488407ab6daf4f1df2756aaa1cdd","tid":995740,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"67c8590fd7d79135aac34e196b572f444535cae0","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c188d338267b92721a5c56a873b209b7a271513","tid":995740,"uid":89514,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"此話何解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得訓覺會去左另一個平行世界<br />\n有d事發生左 當時人話唔知 <br />\nEg 講左某d野<br />\n<br />\n又成日有似曾相識畫面<br />\nEg 打lol 同英同位同事件<br />\n2~12個禮拜會有1次重演<br />\n<br />\n甚至寵物小精靈填色比賽單野<br />\n我有印象我早差唔多成年前睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣冇人討論"},{"pid":"2ce8845282cf27ff7aa030ac8ed6676499e6f96c","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"23da5557fa306ff5052c7dba6d3003342c1fdbd1","tid":995740,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"我都相信時間只係人發明出黎既概念<br />\n世界本無時間 只有此時此刻 一直運轉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死後既世界更多關於信仰既問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"現階段仲在生一定係信仰問題<br />\n但真相只有一個 好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講起信仰我又覺得好有趣<br />\n世界好多嘢都係建基於信仰<br />\n唔講宗教嗰啲<br />\n人同人嘅關係係信<br />\n物質又係信<br />\n點解十蚊紙又係值十蚊 十蚊銀又係值十蚊？<br />\n<br />\n點解黃金 鑽石會值錢？<br />\n難開採？點解會有物以罕為貴呢樣嘢？<br />\n以前人用貝殼做交易 都係因為個個人都信佢嘅價值<br />\n難保一日人類唔再相信黃金嘅價值<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢啲信仰係點建立出嚟？"},{"pid":"73edc16b632667d63aef898048e4f0b437c26a09","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6468da49f111488407ab6daf4f1df2756aaa1cdd","tid":995740,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"67c8590fd7d79135aac34e196b572f444535cae0","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c188d338267b92721a5c56a873b209b7a271513","tid":995740,"uid":89514,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"此話何解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得訓覺會去左另一個平行世界<br />\n有d事發生左 當時人話唔知 <br />\nEg 講左某d野<br />\n<br />\n又成日有似曾相識畫面<br />\nEg 打lol 同英同位同事件<br />\n2~12個禮拜會有1次重演<br />\n<br />\n甚至寵物小精靈填色比賽單野<br />\n我有印象我早差唔多成年前睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣冇人討論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"你係訓緊嗰陣已經發現 定係訓醒先醒起？"},{"pid":"1d2564214477f584975b40503f8e27781f05d2a6","tid":995740,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"哲學家"},{"pid":"4aca127a4107e60fabfcf4db70470aa77f67b6e4","tid":995740,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"「甚麼是時間？如果沒有人問我，我知道。如果我要向發問者解釋，我則一無所知。」奧古斯丁如是說。<br />\n時間長久以來都是一個惱人的哲學問題。有的哲學家主張時間與事物變化在概念上緊密相連：時間，不外是我們量度事物變化的工具。有的哲學家則認為，「時間」和「變化」，兩個概念並不等同：離開事物的變化，我們仍能理解時間。<br />\n另一方面，我們彷彿每分每秒都經歷着時間的流逝，但時間真的在流動嗎？我們一般覺得，時間像河流一樣，川流不息地往前走。但這樣的理解合理嗎？還是時間根本沒有在流動，只不過像接連翻檢的相簿一樣，是事件發生的先後次序？又抑或，時間只是一種幻覺，根本並不真實？<br />\n今集，我們請來中文大學哲學系教授張錦青，討論時間哲學。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/philosophynight2018/episode/514712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fphilosophynight2018%2Fepisode%2F514712&d=%2Bt8JJVZzEYN6%2Bh2Lyu1Zb8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=fa59d93d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/philosophynight2018/episode/514712</a>"},{"pid":"79dba36714daabe1ccbf33f1035e43c4607c795a","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2564214477f584975b40503f8e27781f05d2a6","tid":995740,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"哲學家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"其實香港有無出過哲學家？<br />\n如果想搵人學多啲呢方面嘅嘢 係咪要讀哲學？"},{"pid":"4b009e7d2722211b3a2197400ea39ac0bb121c80","tid":995740,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73edc16b632667d63aef898048e4f0b437c26a09","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6468da49f111488407ab6daf4f1df2756aaa1cdd","tid":995740,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"67c8590fd7d79135aac34e196b572f444535cae0","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"此話何解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得訓覺會去左另一個平行世界<br />\n有d事發生左 當時人話唔知 <br />\nEg 講左某d野<br />\n<br />\n又成日有似曾相識畫面<br />\nEg 打lol 同英同位同事件<br />\n2~12個禮拜會有1次重演<br />\n<br />\n甚至寵物小精靈填色比賽單野<br />\n我有印象我早差唔多成年前睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣冇人討論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"你係訓緊嗰陣已經發現 定係訓醒先醒起？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"似曾相識係經歷當刻先有感覺<br />\n<br />\n但有時有d夢境係直頭會有感覺<br />\n醒個下會好辛苦"},{"pid":"4e44261ece2e1b2b96788fad77a9a04f384c1f5f","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aca127a4107e60fabfcf4db70470aa77f67b6e4","tid":995740,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"「甚麼是時間？如果沒有人問我，我知道。如果我要向發問者解釋，我則一無所知。」奧古斯丁如是說。<br />\n時間長久以來都是一個惱人的哲學問題。有的哲學家主張時間與事物變化在概念上緊密相連：時間，不外是我們量度事物變化的工具。有的哲學家則認為，「時間」和「變化」，兩個概念並不等同：離開事物的變化，我們仍能理解時間。<br />\n另一方面，我們彷彿每分每秒都經歷着時間的流逝，但時間真的在流動嗎？我們一般覺得，時間像河流一樣，川流不息地往前走。但這樣的理解合理嗎？還是時間根本沒有在流動，只不過像接連翻檢的相簿一樣，是事件發生的先後次序？又抑或，時間只是一種幻覺，根本並不真實？<br />\n今集，我們請來中文大學哲學系教授張錦青，討論時間哲學。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/philosophynight2018/episode/514712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fphilosophynight2018%2Fepisode%2F514712&d=%2Bt8JJVZzEYN6%2Bh2Lyu1Zb8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=fa59d93d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/philosophynight2018/episode/514712</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"返去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該你"},{"pid":"fa7b23a9f186dec8e4725810bf1f0ee3b4a7c800","tid":995740,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"時間只係相對嘅概念"},{"pid":"32763035c45ddd2332880ff903f8d705000be90c","tid":995740,"uid":195396,"like":1,"di